c: 34
v: 3
t: "Those who disbelieve say: \"The Hour will not come to us.\" Say: \"Yes, by my Lord, it will come to you.\" (Allah, He is) the AllKnower of the unseen, not even the weight of an atom (or a small ant) or less than that or greater, escapes from His Knowledge in the heavens or in the earth, but it is in a Clear Book (AlLauh AlMahfuz)"